arStrings.szText: So, what did you write on that piece of wood? Something about fear or cowardice perhaps?
So, what did you write on that little piece of wood? Something about hate or anger perhaps?
So, what did you write on that little piece of wood? Something about hubris or pride perhaps?
So, what did you write on that piece of wood? Something about greed or gluttony perhaps?
So, what did you write on that little piece of wood? I'll bet you didn't write anything at all. I wouldn't blame you.
Well, it matters little I suppose.
